text:
Highly recommend :bee:  The gist is to find as many words as possible using 7 letters, words must be 4 letters or more, all words must contain the center letter, and every day there is at least one “pangram” that uses all the letters. New puzzle every day like wordle. It’s addictive and extremely satisfying.
<https://www.nytimes.com/puzzles/spelling-bee>
